These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: metal, r&b, hip-hop, ambient
1. Music-Genre:r&b is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:ambient is between Music-Genre:metal and Music-Genre:r&b##2
3. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Music-Genre:metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | ambient | r&b | hip-hop |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Color: light-blue, lavender, green, grey
1. Color:light-blue is on the left of Color:grey##1
2. Color:lavender is in an odd position##4
3. Color:lavender is on the left or right of Color:light-blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Color   | lavender | light-blue | grey | green |

 #################################
 
