.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
City: nizza, venice, hamburg, boston
1. City:venice == City:venice##1
2. City:boston is on the left or right of City:hamburg##3
3. City:hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
4. City:nizza is in an even position##4
5. City:boston is on the left of City:venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| City   | hamburg | boston | venice | nizza |

